---
title: Truffle Chicken, Bacon & Mushroom Pot Pie with Filo Pastry & Balsamic Rocket Salad
description: A pot pie is a classic for a reason, it’s unbeatable for nostalgia and cosy vibes. Our one comes with creamy chicken, bacon and
mushroom filling but the hint of truffle makes this pie extra special. So dig in and enjoy this timeless delight!
